SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[AgeAvg], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[Name], [a].[Description], [a].[AgeAvg]
    FROM [Animals] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [i].[FileName], [a0].[Id], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[Animal_Id]
    FROM [AnimalImages] AS [a0]
    LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [a0].[Image_Id] = [i].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[Animal_Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]

SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[Name], [a].[Description], [a].[AgeAvg], [t].[FilePath], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Animals] AS [a]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [i].[FilePath], [a0].[Id], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[Animal_Id]
    FROM [AnimalImages] AS [a0]
    LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [a0].[Image_Id] = [i].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[Animal_Id]
ORDER BY [a].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[Name], [a].[Description], [a].[AgeAvg]
    FROM [Animals] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[Name] LIKE @__name_0_contains ESCAPE N'\'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (

SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[Name], [a].[Description], [a].[AgeAvg], [t].[FilePath], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Animals] AS [a]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [i].[FilePath], [a0].[Id], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[Animal_Id]
    FROM [AnimalImages] AS [a0]
    LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [a0].[Image_Id] = [i].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[Animal_Id]
ORDER BY [a].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Animals] AS [a]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [i].[FilePath], [a0].[Id], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[Animal_Id]
    FROM [AnimalImages] AS [a0]
    LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [a0].[Image_Id] = [i].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[Animal_Id]

SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN [Animals] AS [a0] ON [a].[Animal_Id] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN [Animals] AS [a0] ON [a].[Animal_Id] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Animals] AS [a]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [i].[FileName], [a0].[Id], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[Animal_Id]

SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[Name], [a].[Description], [a].[AgeAvg], [t].[FilePath], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Animals] AS [a]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [i].[FilePath], [a0].[Id], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[Animal_Id]
    FROM [AnimalImages] AS [a0]

) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[Animal_Id]
ORDER BY [a].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[Name], [a].[Description], [a].[AgeAvg], [t].[FileName], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Animals] AS [a]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [i].[FileName], [a0].[Id], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[Animal_Id]
    FROM [AnimalImages] AS [a0]

SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[Name], [a].[Description], [a].[AgeAvg], [t].[FileName], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Animals] AS [a]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [i].[FileName], [a0].[Id], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[Animal_Id]
    FROM [AnimalImages] AS [a0]
    LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [a0].[Image_Id] = [i].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[Animal_Id]
WHERE LOWER([a].[Name]) LIKE @__ToLower_0_contains ESCAPE N'\'
ORDER BY [a].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[Name], [a].[Description], [a].[AgeAvg], [t].[FileName], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Animals] AS [a]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [i].[FileName], [a0].[Id], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[Animal_Id]
    FROM [AnimalImages] AS [a0]
    LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [a0].[Image_Id] = [i].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[Animal_Id]
WHERE LOWER([a].[Name]) LIKE @__ToLower_0_contains ESCAPE N'\'
ORDER BY [a].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[Name], [a].[Description], [a].[AgeAvg], [t].[FilePath], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Animals] AS [a]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [i].[FilePath], [a0].[Id], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[Animal_Id]
    FROM [AnimalImages] AS [a0]
    LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [a0].[Image_Id] = [i].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[Animal_Id]
ORDER BY [a].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[Name], [a].[Description], [a].[AgeAvg], [t].[FilePath], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Animals] AS [a]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [i].[FilePath], [a0].[Id], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[Animal_Id]
    FROM [AnimalImages] AS [a0]

) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[Animal_Id]
ORDER BY [a].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[Name], [a].[Description], [a].[AgeAvg], [t].[FileName], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Animals] AS [a]

SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN [Animals] AS [a0] ON [a].[Animal_Id] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN [Animals] AS [a0] ON [a].[Animal_Id] = [a0].[Id]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN [Animals] AS [a0] ON [a].[Animal_Id] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t].[Id]
